\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Basis-induced uncertainty family.} The adversary starts at the uniform source-support distribution and moves only inside a low-rank subspace generated by trajectory failure coordinates. When positivity is inactive, the resulting support function becomes a mean loss plus a basis-aligned norm penalty.}}{7}{figure.caption.9}\protected@file@percent }
